Vidyard,is,a,video,hosting,platform,with,embedded,analytics,tools,that,helps,businesses,track,and,monetize,video,content,Vidyard,helps,content,marketers,get,the,most,out,of,their,video,assets,by,providing,in,depth,data,on,viewer,behavior,that,can,be,automatically,pushed,into,marketing,automation,systems,and,CRMs,Vidyard,offers,their,video,solutions,to,developers,via,a,simple,REST,API,Additional,information,about,the,API,is,available,by,request